This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with object detection using deep neural networks. Additionally, it may also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories as it involves training a deep learning framework. The Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category is also a possibility as the paper mentions the use of a gating network, which is a type of neural network. Finally, the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category is also a possibility as the paper deals with object detection in images.
